From f1fbf9280465777c53573d8a19a87930dd7edd4c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 21 Apr 2025 19:19:42 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Remove wifi7 header files from common code

Remove wifi7 specific header files from common code,
and make required changes in corresponding files
to achieve this.

Patch-dependency:
0114-0015-wifi-ath12k-Segregate-the-common-and-wifi7-specific-.patch

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
